-- BAA Funding Ltd. Said to Plan Sale of Class B Bonds in Pounds
-- B y   B e n   M a r t i n
-- 2012-03-13T09:46:46Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-03-13/baa-funding-ltd-said-to-plan-sale-of-class-b-bonds-in-pounds.html
BAA Funding Ltd. plans to sell
class B bonds in pounds, according to a banker involved in the
transaction.  The company hired Bank of America Corp., Lloyds Banking
Group Plc, Morgan Stanley and  Banco Santander SA (SAN)  for the deal,
the banker said.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Ben Martin at 
 bmartin38@bloomberg.net  